    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require a Guard/Train Manager on every train",
        "additional_details": "Rail reform taking place and threat Driver Only Operated (DOO) trains. This would be a disaster for rail.\r\n\r\nThe guard is vital, leads in charge whenever an onboard emergency occurs, operational such a fire or medical, passengers or criminal.\r\n\r\nGuards lead evacuations, assists the driver in train movement, trained to rules, assist vulnerable passengers, carry out train protection and use G-SMR with signallers and do revenue.\r\n\r\nDOO discriminates against passengers requiring assistance, especially at unmanned stations",
        "background": "Require that every train has a guaranteed safety critical guard/train manager onboard as mandatory for all train operating companies. Prevent the use of Driver Only Operated trains",
